<p>Here&#8217;s a nice little graph showing the prices of gaming consoles over the years. The second one even takes inflation into account.</p>
<p>Personally I don&#8217;t care for the blu-ray and hard-drive extras, most likely it will end up being crippled anyways so that the PS3 unit doesn&#8217;t compete with higher-end players sony will probably make.</p>
<p>And honestly I don&#8217;t see little kids convincing their parents to pay 425 quid for a gaming console with the argument &#8220;Yeah mom, but it can play blu-ray as well.&#8221;</p>
